title: Paige Spiranac’s Workout Uniform Is Incredibly Revealing
text:
(Photo by David Cannon/Getty Images) 5425071 
Paige Spiranac doesn’t like wearing a lot of clothing when she works out. 
The blonde bombshell posted a photo of herself in a sports bra and skintight workout gear on Instagram Monday. (SLIDESHOW: 42 Times Arianny Celeste Went Topless O A photo posted by Paige Spiranac (@_paige.renee) on Jan 16, 2017 at 10:41am PST 
Spiranac’s golf career is steadily growing, but she’s been a star on social media for years. Click an image below for larger version.
